Card Name: What is this
Card Description:
This is a board for **mapping user stories** of a **digital product** (*e.g.* website, web-app, mobile app, desktop app, software).

Each of list in this board represent a story of **one** user role in the product (*e.g.* a story of *newbie-trelloist*, a story of *expert-trelloist*, a story of *trello-superadmin*).
List Name: [Template] Briefs

Card Name: When to use this
Card Description: When you have a product with **multiple user roles** and **~~uncertain~~ complex user stories** to work with.
List Name: [Template] Briefs

Card Name: How to use this
Card Description:
1. **List** user roles of your product
2. **Convert** your list of user roles into lists in this board
3. **Breakdown** user roles into goals, into activities, into tasks *(Goal Card -> Activity Card -> Task Card)*.
4. **Label** each card
5. *(optional)* Add some description or information about the card
List Name: [Template] Briefs

Card Name: Who can use this
Card Description: A person/team that want to or already have a product, and doesn't know how big the product really is.
List Name: [Template] Briefs

Card Name: Why use this
Card Description: To avoid product *scope creep* and other problems of defining product requirements.
List Name: [Template] Briefs
